
SUBJECTIVE(2)              silmul_efun              SUBJECTIVE(2)

名稱
     subjective - "provides an appropriate subject pronoun

語法
     string subjective(string gender);

描述
     Provides an appropriate subject pronoun based on  gender  as
     follows:

     "male"    -> "he"  "female"   ->  "she"  "neuter"   ->  "it"
     (other)   -> "sie"

其它參考檔案
     /adm/simul_efun/pronouns.c

作者
     Ichabod@TMI, 3/5/93
     wade@future 4/8/1996 翻譯

MudOS Release 0.9         Last change:                   3-19-93

